mr. joe b &lt;unk&gt; is a 2014 indian bollywood film directed by sameer tiwari , starring arshad warsi , soha ali khan and arshad warsi in the lead roles . the film is produced by soha ali khan under the banner of vishesh films . the film stars soha ali khan , arshad warsi , soha ali khan , arshad warsi , soha ali khan and arshad warsi . the film was released on 3 january 2014 .